data.title: James Foley
data.meta_description: All about James Foley: biography, date of birth and age, place of birth, height, eye color
data.text:
James Foley - American film director and screenwriter. He was born December 28, 1953 in Brooklyn, United States of America.

Best known for his work on films like At Close Range (1986), After Dark, My Sweet (1990), Glengarry Glen Ross (1992) and House of Cards (2013-2018) TV series.
